    {
        "topic": "Division 296 super changes",
        "status": "Current law",
        "effective": "1 July 2026",
        "summary": (
            "Better Targeted Super Concessions is now law. From 1 July 2026, balances above the large super balance "
            "threshold face an extra 15% tax on the proportion of earnings over that threshold, with an additional "
